{"tid":2353303,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"賢學思政 : 「支援在囚手足平台正式上線」","createTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:04.000Z","updateTime":"2021-01-05T18:57:28.000Z","uid":94771,"like":124,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":91,"replies":[{"pid":"05c551d52652149b1ae7de417d898be3d36d2eb8","tid":2353303,"uid":94771,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:04.000Z","msg":"Source : <a href=\"https://t.me/stpoliticism/155\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpoliticism%2F155&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=80ad4efe\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stpoliticism/155</a><br />\n<span class=\"green\"><span class=\"xx-large\"><strong>入面有條片架，<img src=\"/assets/faces/lm2/noodles.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />，有教學架</strong></span></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「支援在囚手足平台正式上線」<br />\n-<br />\n隨著運動進入低潮期，政權開始瘋狂清算，大量手足被還押甚至被判入獄。在暴政之下，他們被視為一個個冰冷的被捕數字，但在香港人的心裡是曾經與我們在街頭並肩作戰、爭取重光的香港兒女。<br />\n<br />\n早前物資收集的街站得到各位街坊的熱烈支持，收集了大量的牆內物資。為了長期幫助有需要的在囚或還押手足，以及有效地分配物資，我們決定成立支援在囚手足的平台。平台的初衷是希望令更多手足的家屬得到幫助，同時呼籲更多市民關注囚權問題。<br />\n<br />\n平台會將收集所得的物資分配給所需的家屬以及負責支援在囚手足的組織。盼望略盡綿薄之力，減輕家屬購買在囚物資的負擔，令眾人能將資源投放於其他同樣重要的領域。<br />\n-<br />\n有需要可於BIO中找到我們的TG連結，TG內將有bot給手足申請在囚物資，亦可若沒tg，亦可私訊我們的Facebook或Instagram 獲取google form連結。<br />\n<br />\n請根據bot的指引或問題提供該手足姓名、在囚編號、收押院所，便可申請在囚物資。核實後我們會將物資放於不同議員的辦事處，屆時會告知領取人議員名稱及詳細地址。<br />\n<br />\n所有資料會嚴密保存，必要時會全數刪除。<br />\n-<br />\n而TG bot亦會解答關於探訪或在囚問題。若對申請物資方法有任何疑問，歡迎於TG bot直接PM我們查詢。<br />\n-<br />\n最後，我們希望眾人明白，在爭取香港民主的路上不只有傳媒大肆報道的政治人物，還有數之不盡的無名英雄。懇請各位對所有的在囚人士繼續保持高度關注，讓他們在聚光燈下減少受到不公平待遇的機會，同時亦感激所有協助我們的人士。<br />\n<br />\n香港人，毋放棄。<br />\n-<br />\nInstagram：<a href=\"https://instagram.com/st_politicism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Finstagram.com%2Fst_politicism&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=ba93105d\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://instagram.com/st_politicism</a><br />\nFacebook：<a href=\"https://fb.me/stpoliticism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffb.me%2Fstpoliticism&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=120c9943\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://fb.me/stpoliticism</a><br />\nTelegram：<a href=\"https://t.me/stpoliticism\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Ft.me%2Fstpoliticism&d=zT4eWHrghymhx70gWSuuORURuvs7l%2FVEN9tydxl6KII%3D&h=eb71811a\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://t.me/stpoliticism</a><br />\n<br />\n#賢學思政 #支援在囚手足平台"},{"pid":"afe965e6282a85b8094cfc73ada0939d9a05a305","tid":2353303,"uid":374518,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:17.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9fbff9d236df6ad79ca3d51fd01b2331268dc145","tid":2353303,"uid":204231,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:18.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"68c7a518767c4dc982f1e8f566007db45aceed58","tid":2353303,"uid":307203,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:20.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"ed5e65eea74dfbc82134f0340af0bb53800ebbde","tid":2353303,"uid":183844,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:29.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"514cf9b1ce944b1ca06ddab57011f317061f11ea","tid":2353303,"uid":305767,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"<del></del>"},{"pid":"f567fde6b118969890b3c1878675de0901f60820","tid":2353303,"uid":113187,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-01-04T15:29:48.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/mouse/pray.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces